quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  6,51,"Yikoreshe (Qur’an) uburira babandi bafite ubwoba bwo kuzakoranyirizwa kwa Nyagasani wabo, ubwo nta wundi murinzi utari we (Allah) cyangwa uwabavuganira. (Ibyo bikore) kugira ngo bamutinye"
  6,52,"Kandi ntukirukane babandi basenga Nyagasani wabo mu gitondo na nimugoroba bashaka kwishimirwa nawe 48. Nta cyo ubazwa mu byo bakora, na bo ntacyo babazwa mu byo ukora. Nubirukana uzaba ubaye umwe mu bahemu"
  6,53,"Uko ni na ko bamwe mu bantu twabagize ibigeragezo ku bandi (bamwe tubagira abakire abandi tubagira abakene) kugira ngo (abahakanyi b’abakire) bavuge bati \"Ese aba (bakene b’abemera) ni bo Allah yagabiye (kumuyoboka) muri twe (maze twe aratwihorera)?\" Ese Allah ntazi neza abashimira"
  6,54,"Kandi abemera ibimenyetso byacu nibaza bakugana, ujye ubaramutsa uvuga uti \"Salamu alaykum (Amahoro ya Allah abe kuri mwe)\". Nyagasani wanyu yiyemeje kugira impuhwe kugira ngo uzakora ikibi muri mwe kubera ubujiji, maze nyuma yo kugikora akicuza akanakora ibikorwa byiza (azamubabarire). Mu by’ukuri, we (Allah) ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"
  6,55,"Uko ni na ko dusobanura ibimenyetso, kugira ngo inzira y’inkozi z’ibibi isobanuke"